  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Gust Sprites dart between reach distances, disrupt ranged attackers, and occasionally knock someone flat with a well-timed concentrated blast. They are fragile enough that a determined opponent can end them, fast enough that catching them requires commitment. A Cooperative Gust Sprite uses Air Cushion to protect whoever the summoner indicates between its own attacks — a small but genuine defensive contribution at low tiers.</p>"
